  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Make possible 1st years of school in mother tongue</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Bicol, Philippines, families communicate with their children in one of 20 local languages and dialects. But when the youngsters start school they suddenly encounter teachers who speak to them in English and Tagalog, two languages which they hardly know, and this makes learning difficult. It&apos;s very important to design a writing system for these native languages. With your help, 72,214 students in 192 schools will receive their first school instruction in a language more familiar to them.</narrative>
  </description>
